Install checkstyle plugin:
https://marketplace.eclipse.org/content/checkstyle-plug
Set default style to Google style screenshot https://www.screencast.com/t/sU5U9JxaS
Turn on  print margin: General -> Editors -> Text Editors -> Show Print Margin
Set up import order: https://www.screencast.com/t/zehl05Pm
Switch Eclipse to use spaces: https://www.screencast.com/t/A2Up4wxId